Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why Onee-chan was riding...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in Kagawa's car that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:45.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:51.78,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:57.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:03.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:11.25,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.97,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:21.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.70,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:49.58,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:45.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:51.78,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:57.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:03.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:11.25,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.97,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:21.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.70,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:49.58,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:05.14,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)\fscx113.75\fscy103.75\pos(159,384)}Episode 11 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:04.43,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day two years ago, I was with Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were both out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't called or texted her, so Onee-chan was feeling down all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been obsessed with your cell phone this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should just apologize already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when he drove by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's ex. The worst man ever, who had a habit of beating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? You're awfully cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your little boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his name again? Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left you alone on a beautiful day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had also completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July 29th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Onee-chan's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense why she was waiting for her cell phone to ring all day, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got into his car over a simple "happy birthday"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she'd go all the way to his house with a "Merry Christmas"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and straight to a hotel with a simple "I love you, let's get back together."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no saving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...apologized to her sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried calling her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the things she left behind, I checked Onee-chan's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you didn't want to text her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important things should be spoken out loud, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've wanted to apologize, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, she didn't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called at 4:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conveniently, that was when she was out driving with Kagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's accident was at 4:38 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows why Onee-chan didn't pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling Yano this sort of stuff now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to finally come tell him something from two years ago now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to confuse him with all of this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to get out of this, Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So relax and go back inside like a good girl, Takahashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's my fault she was riding in his car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I'm cold-hearted for not going to the funeral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I wasn't with her on her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, tell me why she didn't answer her phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't pick it up because she was with Kagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got what she deserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty rude way of speaking about the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she's dead doesn't mean her sins have gotten lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after she started going out with me, she was never through with Kagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about your sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your own sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten about that day two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, Mom will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black cat. A really small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's... Friday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black cats are bad luck when they cross your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been like this the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get cold feet or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... hadn't forgotten about Onee-chan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed both me and her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you just try to use me as a replacement for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly how you want it to, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lighten your sin a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Onee-chan's incoming call history...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a lot were from Kagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like they were talking all summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She betrayed you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yamamoto-san go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me with the corner of your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so fast to throw things at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I an outsider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you let me hear what she had to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hiding anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said there'd be no secrets between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me not to betray you, but you go and betray me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, betraying someone isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell you what it means to betray someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's when you never treat someone special, walk all over him, tear him to pieces, and then abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell how special you are to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell how hard I'm trying to keep us together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When have I ever betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever toss you away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever toss you away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Yano think Nana-san tossed him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's when you never treat someone special, walk all over him, tear him to pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought such words could come from Yano's mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get closer to Yano's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't loving him enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't my love become his strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely don't do something stupid like tell Takahashi about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try telling her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret it for rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just with Yamamoto that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you regret it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret anything I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never have, never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hiding it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to see her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll cry, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm not going to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like I... screwed up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda hard to talk to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it yesterday and today this whole time, and now it's lunch break already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana! Everyone's going to play dodgeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I have to take care of the class's day book, so go on without me.
