Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happened yesterday seems so unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano and Yamamoto are pretending it didn't happen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your English book yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need your text book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be in trouble in fifth period without it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan, they're gonna call on you today, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you couldn't do your homework since you didn't have your textbook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that must suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:32.63,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.845\b1\c&H404E61&\fscx226.25\fscy207.5\pos(99,456)}Completely\Nforgot\Nabout it
