Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be called on today, so I translated all of the sentences for you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote them all out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was up until 2 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I just can't hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, your drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at it, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's awful at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... he did all this for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more than anyone else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you, I don't like being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand what I'm trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's three choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One. I confessed my love to Yamamoto, and was turned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two. Yamamoto confessed her love to me, and I turned her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Yamamoto and I were in love with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was just a warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One. I sexually harassed Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... two. Yamamoto stalked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're still in the middle of the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you're just trying to sneak out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never intended to discuss this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too weird, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might think number three's the weirdest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Yamamoto and I had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nothing but weird ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you could think up something that weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that third one... Even if you were joking, that's just sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret it for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret anything I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never have, never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like I... screwed up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like I did something stupid.
