Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:48.43,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hizashi mo mijikaku itsuka zurete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:56.81,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no basu wa kawaranai machi
