Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:50.53,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari wa onaji na no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:24:00.54,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshiii kimochii anata no shisen wa ima mienakute
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:30.57,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari wa onaji na no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:38.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikitai basho wa namattetatte iin da yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:47.42,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari wa onaji na no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:57.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshiii kimochii anata no shisen wa ima mienakute
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:40.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the season have changed slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:48.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sunbeams have thinned and will one day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:56.81,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was relieved, knowing our bus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:03.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,was riding through our unchanged city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:12.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You always gaze up at me from outside my window
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:21.33,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I mimic you by doing the same
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:33.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:42.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the place we want to go to has gotten dull, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:50.53,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:24:00.54,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel love for you, but you're no longer looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:30.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:38.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the place we want to go to has gotten dull, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:47.42,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:57.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel love for you, but you're no longer looking at me.
