Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:07.27,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:11.36,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.36,0:25:14.86,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.86,0:25:17.83,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry\N I can't keep our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.67,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.67,0:25:28.59,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...happy dreams.
